Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:06.16,default,,0,0,0,,Special Expansion Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:09.36,default,,0,0,0,,First up is the Kouhaku Uta Gassen Document.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:16.01,default,,0,0,0,,Unreleased video that was not broadcasted in the 60-minute special broadcasted the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.66,default,,0,0,0,,30 seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.82,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:25.05,default,,0,0,0,,After Kouhaku's appearance, Captain Sakurai called out his members.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.71,default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:28.99,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.32,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.08,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.52,default,,0,0,0,,This is absolutely good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.05,default,,0,0,0,,Just once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.49,default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:37.36,default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:40.54,default,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, the members' true feelings burst out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:41.71,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.89,default,,0,0,0,,Last December, they entered the Under Live held at the Nippon Budokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.82,default,,0,0,0,,Complete report behind the scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.52,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:56.79,default,,0,0,0,,Daihankyou's Maid Conto Series, the latest work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:00.47,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:03.67,default,,0,0,0,,Tadio Live will perform two songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.23,default,,0,0,0,,Pop! Pop! Pop! Pop! Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:24.19,default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, it's about time for the real show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:24.95,default,,0,0,0,,Nene
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.79,default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the lyrics of POPPY POPPAPA?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:30.81,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, POPPY POPPAPA is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:34.69,default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I still don't remember the lyrics of POPPY POPPAPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:40.53,default,,0,0,0,,POPPY POPPAPA is good, but last year's KOUHAKU was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:46.94,default,,0,0,0,,The last boss, Sachiko Kobayashi's costume was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.59,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:50.70,default,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:53.13,default,,0,0,0,,That's POPPY PAPAPA!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:02:02.70,default,,0,0,0,,I was saying it in a tone that was amazing, but I don't think that's what Poppipappaba means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:08.69,default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that if you convert Nogizaka to Pagyo, it comes from the part where it becomes Poppipapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.41,default,,0,0,0,,Look at Bubi-papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:18.79,default,,0,0,0,,She said it in a tone that she didn't know, but that's also different, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.79,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.79,default,,0,0,0,,Maya, have you eaten your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.19,default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.09,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.69,default,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten either, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:26.39,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.89,default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten anything since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.09,default,,0,0,0,,Popi-Papapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:35.97,default,,0,0,0,,I said it in a tone that made me hungry, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:39.59,default,,0,0,0,,that's not what popi-papapa means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.59,default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.85,default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not the time to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.85,default,,0,0,0,,It's our important situation, so
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.35,default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't we use it in a rough way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.35,default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.24,default,,0,0,0,,I've been having stiff shoulders lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.78,default,,0,0,0,,I want to get a massage, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:01.16,default,,0,0,0,,I've been having stiff shoulders since I was over 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.12,default,,0,0,0,,I also have stiff shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.83,default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.83,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:07.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting old!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:08.97,default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:09.97,default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.97,default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:11.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.35,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.61,default,,0,0,0,,Pop! Pop! Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.28,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.69,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
