Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.05,default,,0,0,0,,Pony Pony Six
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.75,default,,0,0,0,,Piano Guitar Pony Six
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.45,default,,0,0,0,,40, 46
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.12,default,,0,0,0,,Miyano Kizaku 46
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.94,default,,0,0,0,,P-P-P-P-P-P-P-46
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.50,default,,0,0,0,,If it's a person who understands, it's fine to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.40,default,,0,0,0,,It's a pure word
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,Close the door that you don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.43,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:40.93,default,,0,0,0,,You're dead
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:23.76,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.58,default,,0,0,0,,Piano Kisaku 46
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:29.32,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's have some fun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.80,default,,0,0,0,,No one can beat us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:36.30,default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't know each other, we can understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:44.58,default,,0,0,0,,Let's fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.69,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.39,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:13.61,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.77,default,,0,0,0,,Piano guitar for 46
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.27,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.65,default,,0,0,0,,What is what is shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.65,default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what is that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.65,default,,0,0,0,,What is shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:23.65,default,,0,0,0,,What what what what what what is what is shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.19,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.60,default,,0,0,0,,He made it to the semi-final!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.25,default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:07.80,default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the unreleased scenes that couldn't be aired last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.98,default,,0,0,0,,December 21st
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.46,default,,0,0,0,,The members who performed at the Budokan on this day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.10,default,,0,0,0,,Even after a full-fledged live,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.63,default,,0,0,0,,These six went to NHK in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:40.51,default,,0,0,0,,Kouhaku is waiting for him as a challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.04,default,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything like this, so I'm going to jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.60,default,,0,0,0,,I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.60,default,,0,0,0,,What? It's a live broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.84,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.95,default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of live broadcasts at night, but I don't think I've been on TV much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.95,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.45,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.45,default,,0,0,0,,Since I turned 18, I've never been on a live broadcast at midnight on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.45,default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly started to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.45,default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.45,default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:04.95,default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.37,default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the unreleased scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:17.02,default,,0,0,0,,Kazumi Takayama went to the same high school as a famous artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.21,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's like Kailanba
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:25.87,default,,0,0,0,,Kazumi Takayama said he was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:31.75,default,,0,0,0,,They collected money and gave us flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.09,default,,0,0,0,,I got a message from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.47,default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.61,default,,0,0,0,,There will be four of us this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.61,default,,0,0,0,,Four of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.61,default,,0,0,0,,From X JAPAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.63,default,,0,0,0,,The two of you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.43,default,,0,0,0,,Yusuke-san and Toshi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:49.61,default,,0,0,0,,Takayama is the same as Yoshiki and Toshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:54.16,default,,0,0,0,,And there are 7 strange things about this high school
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.79,default,,0,0,0,,It's a clear color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:03.60,default,,0,0,0,,The piano is sleeping somewhere in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.93,default,,0,0,0,,It's like a crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.93,default,,0,0,0,,That's what you choose, right, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.93,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.93,default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.30,default,,0,0,0,,Arriving at NHK at 11 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.81,default,,0,0,0,,The live broadcast is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.00,default,,0,0,0,,will appear on the show Kouhaku Sendenbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.45,default,,0,0,0,,Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.20,default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.48,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.73,default,,0,0,0,,Then, here too, a message related to X JAPAN was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.91,default,,0,0,0,,Takayama-san can't be here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:40.88,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.31,default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.86,default,,0,0,0,,December 28th
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.60,default,,0,0,0,,3 days until the show
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.98,default,,0,0,0,,These 6 members are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.37,default,,0,0,0,,He will perform as the back dancer of Ayako Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.15,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.17,default,,0,0,0,,Reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.44,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.42,default,,0,0,0,,Today's choreographer is Natsu Mayumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.69,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:14.47,default,,0,0,0,,Natsu Mayumi-sensei also taught Morning Musume and AKB48.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.68,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.93,default,,0,0,0,,The choreography uses sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.75,default,,0,0,0,,The members who can't get used to the movement
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.24,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.94,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.21,default,,0,0,0,,This is the front of the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.98,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.07,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.83,default,,0,0,0,,They have to finish it in three days from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.22,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.49,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:42.03,default,,0,0,0,,This is how it was broadcasted last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.18,default,,0,0,0,,Here's a scene you won't regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:49.59,default,,0,0,0,,The members who are desperate to learn from Natsu-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.51,default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:51.80,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:52.59,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.83,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.20,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.99,default,,0,0,0,,Back, back, back, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:11:59.63,default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.34,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.00,default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:04.60,default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.98,default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.74,default,,0,0,0,,It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:10.03,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.97,default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to dance as he was taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.45,default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.40,default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.40,default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.99,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.37,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.94,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:30.71,default,,0,0,0,,Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.70,default,,0,0,0,,It's a good place to dance, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.44,default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you're going to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.54,default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.36,default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time dancing with a sense of dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:44.67,default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to figure out what it's going to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:48.67,default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to figure out what it's going to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.64,default,,0,0,0,,I won't close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.75,default,,0,0,0,,Keep it open
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.61,default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if you could make it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.16,default,,0,0,0,,I will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.11,default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:05.67,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.53,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:11.41,default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.96,default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.06,default,,0,0,0,,We are Nobizaka48
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it like this all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.59,default,,0,0,0,,Your face is going to be a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.67,default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the most visible part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.46,default,,0,0,0,,properly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.94,default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to show you my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.54,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.76,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:31.76,default,,0,0,0,,O.T.6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.76,default,,0,0,0,,O.T.6?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.76,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.76,default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.76,default,,0,0,0,,I said O.T.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.76,default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.76,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.76,default,,0,0,0,,How many times did you make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.76,default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.76,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.40,default,,0,0,0,,The choreography is gradually coming together
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.95,default,,0,0,0,,This person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.17,default,,0,0,0,,The left side of the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:52.91,default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:53.91,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.05,default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.18,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.44,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:08.97,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai-san always messes up the shape of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.55,default,,0,0,0,,And then, the 4-hour shake-off is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.92,default,,0,0,0,,I used to like Moose very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:25.92,default,,0,0,0,,I was very nervous from the beginning to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.92,default,,0,0,0,,But he was a kind person, so I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:36.34,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai was moved to meet Natsu-sensei, who was more worried about dancing than about dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.02,default,,0,0,0,,December 29th, 9AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.13,default,,0,0,0,,Two days left until the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.11,default,,0,0,0,,The first rehearsal at NHK Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.41,default,,0,0,0,,If you want to enter, please enter in the position of the intro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.99,default,,0,0,0,,Please watch one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.62,default,,0,0,0,,I think it will become a investment as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.34,default,,0,0,0,,This is the only time you can do it with sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:04.22,default,,0,0,0,,One more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:05.65,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.81,default,,0,0,0,,Nogizaka 46 can use the stage for about 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:14.76,default,,0,0,0,,He checked his standing position and his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.02,default,,0,0,0,,Next, MC interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.81,default,,0,0,0,,While doing a schedule of minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.39,default,,0,0,0,,there is also a surprise from the members!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.02,default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:35.86,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.52,default,,0,0,0,,It looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.92,default,,0,0,0,,it has a lot of crackers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.35,default,,0,0,0,,IKOMO is today
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:47.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's my birthday, so I want to celebrate it with a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.55,default,,0,0,0,,And this is the end of the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.83,default,,0,0,0,,A scene that won't be revealed from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.93,default,,0,0,0,,The members are waiting for Ikoma-san
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.39,default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.59,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.67,default,,0,0,0,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.48,default,,0,0,0,,Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.79,default,,0,0,0,,You have a good sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.79,default,,0,0,0,,Mine is a little short.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.79,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.42,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.82,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.05,default,,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.46,default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.26,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.95,default,,0,0,0,,Among them are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.61,default,,0,0,0,,This kind of member is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.06,default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.33,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.11,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's going to be really messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.25,default,,0,0,0,,I should make a stamp card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.51,default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.55,default,,0,0,0,,It was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.35,default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.93,default,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.29,default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.01,default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the surprise was a great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:23.99,default,,0,0,0,,Next is the rehearsal of Ayako Fujii's song, but she is worried about her outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.65,default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:34.85,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a lot of clothes that I want to wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.91,default,,0,0,0,,but I think I'm going to compete at the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,This is how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:44.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'm still hiding it, but I can see it when I dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:47.07,default,,0,0,0,,Here comes Ayako Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:50.65,default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Fujii is from Akita Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.01,default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.01,default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.01,default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.01,default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.01,default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.01,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.19,default,,0,0,0,,Kawaii kawaii
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:09.97,default,,0,0,0,,This is what Akita's uncle and aunt are proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.70,default,,0,0,0,,And this is the end of the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.94,default,,0,0,0,,From now on, it's an unreleased scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.41,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.40,default,,0,0,0,,After checking the choreography
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.24,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai has a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.97,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:34.21,default,,0,0,0,,Why are there so many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.40,default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.40,default,,0,0,0,,You are good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.40,default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you should do this on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.31,default,,0,0,0,,I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.06,default,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's so curved
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.06,default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.06,default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen such a curved one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:05.06,default,,0,0,0,,If you try not to bend your stomach, you will make a mistake in your sense
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,If you pay attention to the direction of your sense, your stomach will bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:18.07,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if my body is stiff, but I don't have a good sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:25.04,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, not only Sakurai-san but also Hashimoto-san struggled with the choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:31.61,default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous that I almost forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:38.70,default,,0,0,0,,I make a lot of mistakes every time, but as a result, I often make mistakes because I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:39.70,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:43.61,default,,0,0,0,,She's a number dancer and an OED dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.84,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.84,default,,0,0,0,,I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.84,default,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.84,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.84,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.84,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:20:00.85,default,,0,0,0,,Please don't give me a sudden expression of excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:08.53,default,,0,0,0,,It was the moment when Sakurai-san, who was depressed because the choreography didn't go well, changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:13.13,default,,0,0,0,,And for the first time, they rehearse with Ayako Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.32,default,,0,0,0,,See you in the next video!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:18.16,default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.03,default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.41,default,,0,0,0,,After the rehearsal, the members check the choreography immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.12,default,,0,0,0,,Before the show
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:49.92,default,,0,0,0,,I only have 30 minutes left, so let's concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.11,default,,0,0,0,,The one in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.40,default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.44,default,,0,0,0,,The light is red and it's really strong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:56.56,default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.63,default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:04.44,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't release something, it will be a little hazy, so take a little more accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.67,default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to practice putting my emotions into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.45,default,,0,0,0,,I'm a 30-year-old kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:16.56,default,,0,0,0,,Basically, you step, step, and take the accent from your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:17.50,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:23.51,default,,0,0,0,,It's not about the technique of the body, but how do you get it out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.93,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please, more, so, like that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:28.75,default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:33.46,default,,0,0,0,,If you think, please, more, that's why, you might get a little emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:39.54,default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you say, step and stretch, step and stretch, step and stretch, this will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:43.05,default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me that you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.73,default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:50.26,default,,0,0,0,,With Natsu-sensei's guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.76,default,,0,0,0,,The members' movements have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.16,default,,0,0,0,,You're older than me, Hajimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:03.13,default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a woman's passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:05.45,default,,0,0,0,,You have a good sense of humor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.56,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it look more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.41,default,,0,0,0,,There are some parts that come off easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:13.59,default,,0,0,0,,What I'm good at is very beautiful, but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.05,0:22:14.55,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.43,default,,0,0,0,,If you think you're good at it, it makes you feel a little bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:18.23,default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:20.62,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you watch it, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:25.36,default,,0,0,0,,They were the members who taught Natsu-sensei very important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.03,default,,0,0,0,,The day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.37,default,,0,0,0,,When the members gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.82,default,,0,0,0,,Checking the choreography immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:38.50,default,,0,0,0,,This is good for both legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:43.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.13,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:46.78,default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.32,default,,0,0,0,,You don't look nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.53,default,,0,0,0,,Right before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:54.28,default,,0,0,0,,The engine unites the hearts of 37 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:59.38,default,,0,0,0,,Today, all the members will be participating in the karate class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:06.49,default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot, but we've all done our best, so I think we can go home like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:10.50,default,,0,0,0,,I'm having so much fun today that I'm going to give it all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:11.35,default,,0,0,0,,Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.81,default,,0,0,0,,Let's stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:15.44,default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:17.33,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:25.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:28.11,default,,0,0,0,,Kabate! Kabate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.67,default,,0,0,0,,Here's the unreleased scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:38.80,default,,0,0,0,,Trouble occurs just before the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:44.40,default,,0,0,0,,A penlight was given to the members waiting for the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:45.14,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:46.16,default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:50.11,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's not on now, but it's automatically controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:56.57,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the color will change automatically, so please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:00.12,default,,0,0,0,,This is a penlight that glows by remote control.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:04.53,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:06.64,default,,0,0,0,,This is my color, Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:08.64,default,,0,0,0,,Lanin color.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:10.64,default,,0,0,0,,Lanin color.
