Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.63,0:36:27.83,default,,0,0,0,,You don't need it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.03,0:36:28.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.05,0:36:30.05,default,,0,0,0,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.05,0:36:31.05,default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.05,0:36:33.05,default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.19,0:36:37.29,default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.07,0:36:42.19,default,,0,0,0,,We've been cheering for you guys for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.69,0:36:47.29,default,,0,0,0,,Master, this robot costs 350,000 yen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.29,0:36:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,That's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.39,0:36:50.09,default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.09,0:36:51.35,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.35,0:36:52.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's a rental fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.25,0:36:53.89,default,,0,0,0,,That's too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.89,0:36:56.69,default,,0,0,0,,It costs 350,000 yen per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:59.79,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the price, but it's very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.93,0:37:01.71,default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.82,0:37:04.38,default,,0,0,0,,Not only the room, but also the money is dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.48,0:37:04.98,default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.37,0:37:09.47,default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant. I was about to be taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.47,0:37:12.03,default,,0,0,0,,Master, is there anything else you'd like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:15.63,default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.77,0:37:18.47,default,,0,0,0,,Can you clean it normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.47,0:37:19.57,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.69,0:37:22.09,default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.33,0:37:23.83,default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.57,0:37:29.75,default,,0,0,0,,I was finally motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.08,0:37:33.14,default,,0,0,0,,Can you clean the dirty part of this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.37,0:37:35.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's cleaning from a dirty place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.74,0:37:37.74,default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.92,0:37:39.92,default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 100 points for your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.92,0:37:41.92,default,,0,0,0,,The dirty part is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.43,0:37:43.41,default,,0,0,0,,I can say almost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.16,0:37:46.16,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.21,0:37:45.71,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.85,0:37:51.25,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.48,0:37:53.80,default,,0,0,0,,This is the best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:55.96,default,,0,0,0,,You stop too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.16,0:37:57.26,default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.41,0:38:00.21,default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.21,0:38:02.45,default,,0,0,0,,It's your chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:03.63,default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.15,0:38:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,Your hair will grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.70,0:38:11.22,default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.42,0:38:14.22,default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's better for us to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.22,0:38:16.52,default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't remember such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.52,0:38:19.12,default,,0,0,0,,Don't change! It's okay! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.12,0:38:23.42,default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please throw away what you don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.42,0:38:24.42,default,,0,0,0,,It's around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.64,0:38:28.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw away the things I don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.47,0:38:31.01,default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the way of cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.01,0:38:33.51,default,,0,0,0,,I told you to throw away the things you don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.51,0:38:34.89,default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean I don't need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.89,0:38:36.65,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I definitely don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.65,0:38:38.41,default,,0,0,0,,No, I asked you to throw away the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.71,0:38:41.71,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:44.45,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! You're not trash, you're trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.45,0:38:45.95,default,,0,0,0,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.95,0:38:47.59,default,,0,0,0,,And you're good at it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.59,0:38:49.15,default,,0,0,0,,So it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.15,0:38:52.53,default,,0,0,0,,It's about saying, please throw away what you don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.67,0:38:55.19,default,,0,0,0,,Can I get rid of this camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.33,0:39:01.65,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I haven't used it much lately, but it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.92,0:39:04.78,default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't clean your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.18,0:39:07.22,default,,0,0,0,,Master, do you know Danshari?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.45,0:39:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.77,0:39:13.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of life to get rid of things you don't use and refresh your room and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.01,0:39:15.85,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Donshari.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:17.16,default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:18.93,default,,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of this camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.65,0:39:21.65,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.21,0:39:23.01,default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.01,0:39:23.95,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.22,0:39:25.62,default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of the fashion department.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.89,0:39:28.07,default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Then please dispose of this camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.07,0:39:28.57,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.89,0:39:30.23,default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.23,0:39:31.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.68,0:39:32.58,default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.32,default,,0,0,0,,It's creepy and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.65,0:39:36.05,default,,0,0,0,,I just got rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.05,0:39:38.35,default,,0,0,0,,That's fast! Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.46,0:39:38.96,default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:40.44,default,,0,0,0,,You sold it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.61,0:39:41.41,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:43.21,default,,0,0,0,,You sold that camera, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.21,0:39:44.35,default,,0,0,0,,What did I sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.77,0:39:48.27,default,,0,0,0,,So the money you have is the money you sold the camera for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.27,0:39:49.27,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.27,0:39:50.99,default,,0,0,0,,Then what is that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.58,0:39:54.52,default,,0,0,0,,There's a strange old man, and that camera and money...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.65,0:39:56.33,default,,0,0,0,,I said I wanted to exchange it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.54,0:39:58.34,default,,0,0,0,,I thought I didn't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.59,0:39:59.59,default,,0,0,0,,I've exchanged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.59,0:40:01.59,default,,0,0,0,,That's what you call selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.59,0:40:04.09,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with someone else's stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:05.09,default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.09,0:40:05.59,default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.59,0:40:07.59,default,,0,0,0,,You can dispose of this trash can as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.59,0:40:08.59,default,,0,0,0,,It's not a trash can!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.59,0:40:10.59,default,,0,0,0,,It's a savings box!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.78,0:40:11.86,default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.25,0:40:14.35,default,,0,0,0,,You have clothes you want, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.35,0:40:15.89,default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.09,0:40:16.71,default,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.89,0:40:20.07,default,,0,0,0,,I saved 500 yen and finally got 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.51,0:40:21.97,default,,0,0,0,,Please get rid of this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.97,0:40:23.91,default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.91,0:40:25.23,default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.60,0:40:26.86,default,,0,0,0,,It's a robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.10,0:40:28.98,default,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is a robbery!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.43,0:40:32.43,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.94,0:40:32.60,default,,0,0,0,,You've done both, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.50,0:40:36.78,default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make a big deal out of it later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.94,0:40:40.94,default,,0,0,0,,The way he stutters is old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.94,0:40:42.94,default,,0,0,0,,And he doesn't make any whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.71,0:40:47.31,default,,0,0,0,,Master, please get rid of this car's key.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.55,0:40:50.01,default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to sell your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.01,0:40:53.83,default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a girlfriend to sit on the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.83,0:40:56.09,default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste to have a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.54,0:40:59.64,default,,0,0,0,,You're terrible. That was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:01.46,default,,0,0,0,,Please get rid of this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.46,0:41:03.06,default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:03.86,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.86,0:41:06.36,default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.36,0:41:07.54,default,,0,0,0,,It's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.29,0:41:11.35,default,,0,0,0,,I think I've put a girl on it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.49,0:41:13.33,default,,0,0,0,,You only brought the key. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.33,0:41:15.39,default,,0,0,0,,The car was too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.87,0:41:16.89,default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.89,0:41:19.53,default,,0,0,0,,You just said you couldn't sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:21.97,default,,0,0,0,,Master, do you have anything else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.49,0:41:25.59,default,,0,0,0,,I lost both my camera and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.73,0:41:27.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.07,0:41:28.17,default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:32.02,default,,0,0,0,,Can you clean up this dirty place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.64,0:41:34.74,default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.74,0:41:37.08,default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.08,0:41:38.54,default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.88,0:41:40.50,default,,0,0,0,,May I borrow your chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.83,0:41:44.17,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. It's expensive, so I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.86,0:41:46.12,default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.32,0:41:49.30,default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.55,0:41:52.79,default,,0,0,0,,It's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.09,0:41:55.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:01.51,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.93,0:42:05.93,default,,0,0,0,,Wait wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.93,0:42:08.77,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.77,0:42:11.61,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look at me with that weird look.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.61,0:42:12.71,default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.93,0:42:15.35,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to clean anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.35,0:42:18.11,default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.46,0:42:19.86,default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.41,0:42:21.81,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.21,0:42:23.01,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.39,0:42:25.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's a tsundere!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.39,0:42:28.13,default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:30.51,default,,0,0,0,,Master, there's something on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.69,0:42:31.19,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.90,0:42:33.90,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.89,0:42:34.17,default,,0,0,0,,It's my chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.17,0:42:35.29,default,,0,0,0,,My chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.29,0:42:36.09,default,,0,0,0,,It's sticking out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.32,0:42:38.92,default,,0,0,0,,Master, is there anything else you'd like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.92,0:42:40.32,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.32,0:42:41.72,default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:44.96,default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have the floor all decorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.44,0:42:47.44,default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.68,0:42:50.56,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.42,0:42:53.24,default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm going to put a band-aid on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.41,0:42:54.07,default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.39,0:42:56.73,default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.12,0:42:59.12,default,,0,0,0,,Miya-chan! Miya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.32,0:43:01.52,default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:05.54,default,,0,0,0,,AHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.01,0:43:13.01,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.73,0:43:16.19,default,,0,0,0,,Master, this is the purpose, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.19,0:43:18.05,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.05,0:43:20.93,default,,0,0,0,,It's a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.93,0:43:25.67,default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, don't throw things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.95,0:43:27.95,default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.61,0:43:30.61,default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.61,0:43:32.61,default,,0,0,0,,Who hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.61,0:43:34.61,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.17,0:43:36.17,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.17,0:43:38.17,default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.59,0:43:39.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.71,0:43:41.71,default,,0,0,0,,It's on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.71,0:43:43.71,default,,0,0,0,,And the important thing is that the clock isn't on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.71,0:43:45.71,default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.71,0:43:47.71,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.81,0:43:48.51,default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.51,0:43:50.77,default,,0,0,0,,The fee is 2.6 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.68,0:43:52.18,default,,0,0,0,,It's high!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.61,0:43:54.61,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.53,0:43:55.53,default,,0,0,0,,But I'll pay for it! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.53,0:43:57.83,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.17,0:44:01.91,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.33,0:44:03.87,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.82,0:44:07.82,default,,0,0,0,,Translated by Vortex
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.71,0:44:09.87,default,,0,0,0,,Nagizaka 46!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:18.11,default,,0,0,0,,Next is Captain Sakurai's lecture room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.88,0:44:22.82,default,,0,0,0,,Who will come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.65,0:44:27.65,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.09,0:44:30.83,default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.07,0:44:33.63,default,,0,0,0,,Erika-sama, I'm a little confused about the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.63,0:44:36.25,default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering where it was, so I'm sorry. It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.25,0:44:37.71,default,,0,0,0,,I see, it's your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.71,0:44:39.85,default,,0,0,0,,Here, please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:41.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's like this, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.15,0:44:42.31,default,,0,0,0,,It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.31,0:44:46.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's called a lecture room, so I thought you were staring and waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.39,0:44:48.25,default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's what I should have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.25,0:44:52.45,default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten anything about the concept of this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.45,0:44:57.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I've forgotten, but I feel like I'm in a chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.73,0:44:58.47,default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.88,0:45:07.06,default,,0,0,0,,Since it's a Kouhaku special, this year was the first time you participated in Kouhaku. How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.39,0:45:10.99,default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.13,0:45:11.73,default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.00,0:45:14.74,default,,0,0,0,,When I realized it, it was already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.94,0:45:18.74,default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.88,0:45:20.04,default,,0,0,0,,Were you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.18,0:45:20.78,default,,0,0,0,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.99,0:45:23.15,default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.26,0:45:24.94,default,,0,0,0,,The position when you're waiting is...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.05,0:45:31.09,default,,0,0,0,,It was always close to midsummer, but I cried in midsummer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.52,0:45:32.92,default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.92,0:45:37.80,default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous that I said Iku-chan in the middle of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.80,0:45:41.22,default,,0,0,0,,I was relieved of my nervousness while supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.47,0:45:44.47,default,,0,0,0,,You were nervous, weren't you? I was nervous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.47,0:45:45.47,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.47,0:45:49.47,default,,0,0,0,,It was crazy. You knew I was nervous, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.47,0:45:52.47,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really look at Reika.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.15,0:45:55.15,default,,0,0,0,,So you weren't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.15,0:45:57.15,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wasn't really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.96,0:45:58.96,default,,0,0,0,,I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.96,0:46:00.96,default,,0,0,0,,I relied on you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.96,0:46:01.46,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.82,0:46:02.70,default,,0,0,0,,Did I drop something?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.81,0:46:05.21,default,,0,0,0,,I was relying on you. I was looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.21,0:46:05.71,default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.71,0:46:06.21,default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.37,0:46:07.83,default,,0,0,0,,Eh? From far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.83,0:46:08.73,default,,0,0,0,,From far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.73,0:46:11.33,default,,0,0,0,,That's scary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.33,0:46:12.73,default,,0,0,0,,When I say Iku-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.25,0:46:14.83,default,,0,0,0,,I have to touch that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.83,0:46:16.09,default,,0,0,0,,8 photo albums!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.09,0:46:17.63,default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.89,0:46:19.01,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.01,0:46:20.51,default,,0,0,0,,Erika, you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.51,0:46:22.39,default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.39,0:46:24.51,default,,0,0,0,,And you're in Germany, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.98,0:46:27.78,default,,0,0,0,,That's where you're from, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.93,0:46:28.93,default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.93,0:46:29.93,default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.93,0:46:30.93,default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.93,0:46:31.93,default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.93,0:46:34.93,default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm hearing Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.93,0:46:35.93,default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.93,0:46:36.93,default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.79,0:46:43.05,default,,0,0,0,,I lived until I was 5 years old, and it's been 13 years since I went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.65,0:46:45.11,default,,0,0,0,,It's been 13 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.11,0:46:47.49,default,,0,0,0,,It's been a really long time since I wrote a photo book.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.61,0:46:52.81,default,,0,0,0,,I took the same composition when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.44,0:46:55.00,default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly the same composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.13,0:46:57.73,default,,0,0,0,,I also put those photos in my photo book.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.73,0:46:59.01,default,,0,0,0,,That's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.01,0:47:02.77,default,,0,0,0,,I went around the places I remember and had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.97,0:47:06.05,default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.21,0:47:07.09,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.65,0:47:10.19,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.30,0:47:12.64,default,,0,0,0,,Try on a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.64,0:47:13.80,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.80,0:47:16.94,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you can only see it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.12,0:47:19.58,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you would do it, Iku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.58,0:47:21.58,default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.73,0:47:23.41,default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.71,0:47:24.37,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.96,0:47:26.52,default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.62,0:47:30.86,default,,0,0,0,,It's refreshing, beautiful, cute, and lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.86,0:47:31.80,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.93,0:47:33.23,default,,0,0,0,,I saw it! Just a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.24,0:47:35.74,default,,0,0,0,,No, please, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.03,0:47:36.77,default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.77,0:47:38.37,default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.37,0:47:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.58,0:47:40.58,default,,0,0,0,,Give me your autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.58,0:47:41.58,default,,0,0,0,,I have two autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.58,0:47:42.58,default,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.58,0:47:43.58,default,,0,0,0,,Two autographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.58,0:47:44.58,default,,0,0,0,,I have two autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.58,0:47:45.58,default,,0,0,0,,I have two autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.58,0:47:46.58,default,,0,0,0,,I have two autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.39,0:47:47.89,default,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.89,0:47:48.39,default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.39,0:47:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,You said it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.39,0:47:50.39,default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.39,0:47:51.39,default,,0,0,0,,The rest is that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.65,0:47:53.19,default,,0,0,0,,Nagisaka station
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.31,0:47:54.83,default,,0,0,0,,Hustle bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.33,0:47:57.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's a song by Nogizaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.95,0:47:59.95,default,,0,0,0,,Your Name is Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.95,0:48:01.95,default,,0,0,0,,Did you listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.95,0:48:03.95,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't listen to it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.95,0:48:05.95,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.81,0:48:08.81,default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.09,0:48:12.29,default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.41,0:48:13.35,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.47,0:48:16.37,default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.61,0:48:19.19,default,,0,0,0,,I was scolded for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.58,0:48:20.60,default,,0,0,0,,This is a lecture room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.21,0:48:24.89,default,,0,0,0,,Please report everything to the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.89,0:48:26.55,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.75,0:48:27.75,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.75,0:48:28.75,default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's like a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.75,0:48:29.75,default,,0,0,0,,It's become!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.75,0:48:30.75,default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:32.75,default,,0,0,0,,As expected, thank you, Iku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.75,0:48:42.75,default,,0,0,0,,After all, Iku-chan's piano is one of the weapons that represents the group called Nogizaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.13,0:48:44.17,default,,0,0,0,,How about you, IKU?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.54,0:48:49.94,default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of members, of course there are also student members, but probably the most
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.17,0:48:53.61,default,,0,0,0,,I think they are members who are trying their best to be on the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.61,0:48:55.79,default,,0,0,0,,I think that's true for the fans as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.03,0:48:58.41,default,,0,0,0,,I think everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.78,0:49:00.08,default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.35,0:49:01.79,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.89,0:49:04.71,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.71,0:49:06.59,default,,0,0,0,,But surprisingly
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.01,0:49:08.15,default,,0,0,0,,I was cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.48,0:49:10.80,default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.94,0:49:12.90,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this and that in the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.02,0:49:16.12,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.29,0:49:22.29,default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking that I might be able to come up with a plan, and that it might be the right thing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.29,0:49:24.29,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.29,0:49:29.73,default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I was told that I was off all day, and I didn't have a school or a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.75,0:49:32.37,default,,0,0,0,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.86,0:49:34.62,default,,0,0,0,,I become a lazy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.62,0:49:37.14,default,,0,0,0,,By the way, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.47,0:49:38.91,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there such a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.23,0:49:41.83,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much free time in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.83,0:49:42.53,default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.53,0:49:43.73,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.06,0:49:44.56,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.80,0:49:51.00,default,,0,0,0,,There are times when I finish school early and then go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.55,0:49:54.69,default,,0,0,0,,I don't really go out to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.26,0:49:57.66,default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck at home working.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:49:59.96,default,,0,0,0,,Working? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.06,0:50:01.36,default,,0,0,0,,I usually play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.53,0:50:06.97,default,,0,0,0,,I do my homework and watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.36,0:50:10.58,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.85,0:50:12.39,default,,0,0,0,,I can't move
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.73,0:50:14.05,default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.53,0:50:15.21,default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.42,0:50:17.52,default,,0,0,0,,At times like that, I just eat chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.30,0:50:20.30,default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.99,0:50:22.99,default,,0,0,0,,Intermittent intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.13,0:50:24.85,default,,0,0,0,,Then you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.96,0:50:26.96,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.17,0:50:26.83,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.55,0:50:30.55,default,,0,0,0,,You like to play the piano and sing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.55,0:50:31.55,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.77,0:50:32.27,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.51,0:50:34.57,default,,0,0,0,,After that, I look at things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.10,0:50:36.94,default,,0,0,0,,I see them singing on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.04,0:50:39.10,default,,0,0,0,,I often go to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.20,0:50:39.84,default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.94,0:50:42.00,default,,0,0,0,,They must be getting tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.59,0:50:44.97,default,,0,0,0,,What I want to do the most is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:46.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's like a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.37,0:50:47.41,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.81,0:50:48.81,default,,0,0,0,,Musical?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.81,0:50:49.81,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.81,0:50:50.81,default,,0,0,0,,In the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.94,0:50:52.24,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.24,0:50:55.48,default,,0,0,0,,You're also playing a leading role in Japan, aren't you, Ikuta-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.48,0:50:56.52,default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.80,0:50:58.80,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.69,0:50:59.69,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.01,0:51:12.01,default,,0,0,0,,It's a witch's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.01,0:51:13.01,default,,0,0,0,,Witch's?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.01,0:51:15.01,default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were really hard-working.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.01,0:51:16.01,default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.01,0:51:17.01,default,,0,0,0,,I was watching you up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.18,0:51:17.82,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.82,0:51:18.96,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.77,0:51:20.85,default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.05,0:51:26.35,default,,0,0,0,,The ribbon knight had a big box, and there was a local park.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.35,0:51:28.63,default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.77,0:51:29.77,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.65,0:51:31.25,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.52,0:51:33.52,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.13,0:51:34.13,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.09,0:51:35.35,default,,0,0,0,,For the ribbon, Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.52,0:51:42.48,default,,0,0,0,,It made me feel good to be close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.69,0:51:43.45,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.90,0:51:46.94,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not that much pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.10,0:51:47.60,default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.97,0:51:51.89,default,,0,0,0,,It's fun, so I want to do more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.19,0:51:55.43,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was more curious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.68,0:52:00.52,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you didn't have a hard time because it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.64,0:52:01.14,default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.21,0:52:02.09,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.24,0:52:09.02,default,,0,0,0,,I want to express it in a different way, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.12,0:52:19.12,default,,0,0,0,,I went to Nogizaka when I was in junior high school, so I spent all my junior high and high school years as a student here, and I didn't have the experience that ordinary people have.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.12,0:52:19.62,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.62,0:52:21.74,default,,0,0,0,,So I have to be like that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.17,0:52:28.45,default,,0,0,0,,Even if I try to put out the life of that person, I can't put it out to the depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.45,0:52:31.79,default,,0,0,0,,I think that's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.19,0:52:34.19,default,,0,0,0,,Life experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.62,0:52:36.08,default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.25,0:52:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to express.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.90,0:52:40.62,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.34,0:52:42.30,default,,0,0,0,,From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.91,0:52:44.57,default,,0,0,0,,As Rika Ikuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.44,0:52:46.40,default,,0,0,0,,this year
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.81,0:52:52.87,default,,0,0,0,,It's not a goal. What do you want to be in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.47,0:52:54.85,default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of my teenage years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.97,0:52:56.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn 19 soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.29,0:52:56.79,default,,0,0,0,,That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.18,0:52:58.46,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.65,0:53:00.65,default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.65,0:53:02.65,default,,0,0,0,,It suddenly became a good voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.93,0:53:06.35,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, so now...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.72,0:53:12.54,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to limit myself to this path, but I want to try various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.05,0:53:15.05,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.27,0:53:20.15,default,,0,0,0,,The image of Nogizaka is not so different from the image seen by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.15,0:53:22.15,default,,0,0,0,,So that kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.33,0:53:24.49,default,,0,0,0,,This year, we did a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.21,0:53:27.15,default,,0,0,0,,I hope it changes little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.29,0:53:33.45,default,,0,0,0,,I want more people to think that I'm doing something like this, or that I didn't have this image.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.01,0:53:34.51,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.91,0:53:36.91,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.96,0:53:42.10,default,,0,0,0,,Your future is bright, so I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.49,0:53:44.49,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.49,0:53:46.57,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.25,0:53:50.25,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.40,0:53:51.80,default,,0,0,0,,Nogizaka 46
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.98,0:53:59.48,default,,0,0,0,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.65,0:54:03.99,default,,0,0,0,,Nogizaka Under Live was held for two days in December last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.15,0:54:09.93,default,,0,0,0,,This live is performed by members other than the selection of Nogizaka46.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.53,0:54:14.99,default,,0,0,0,,In 2014, it was held at a handshake event.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.99,0:54:17.55,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.66,0:54:19.54,default,,0,0,0,,The scale is getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.97,0:54:24.59,default,,0,0,0,,Finally, they have arrived at Budokan, which they had been aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.89,0:54:28.89,default,,0,0,0,,This commemorative live will be reported by...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:32.78,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Reika! I'm Yumi Okatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.34,0:54:36.36,default,,0,0,0,,Captain Reika Sakurai and Yumi Wakatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.76,0:54:39.76,default,,0,0,0,,Today, tomorrow, and for the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.76,0:54:41.16,default,,0,0,0,,Underlove is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.16,0:54:42.16,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.37,0:54:43.37,default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.37,0:54:44.37,default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.80,0:54:47.78,default,,0,0,0,,It's cold outside, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.78,0:54:50.04,default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice follow-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.04,0:54:51.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.92,0:54:54.14,default,,0,0,0,,You can say that in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.10,0:55:00.50,default,,0,0,0,,The two are a little unreliable, but will they be able to bring out the charm of the members firmly?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.77,0:55:02.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.89,0:55:05.37,default,,0,0,0,,The highlight of the 5-day concert is...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.73,0:55:11.61,default,,0,0,0,,All participants will perform one song at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.89,0:55:18.03,default,,0,0,0,,In addition, the members have come up with various ideas for the set list.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.88,0:55:23.88,default,,0,0,0,,Based on that, Tokuhai interviews the members before the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.86,0:55:28.44,default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai-san has been watching a lot of UNDERLIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.89,0:55:31.77,default,,0,0,0,,I go to see it every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.77,0:55:35.05,default,,0,0,0,,Underlife is fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.20,0:55:36.84,default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.96,0:55:40.92,default,,0,0,0,,This is a catering black pepper yaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.12,0:55:43.78,default,,0,0,0,,It's a meal for the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.57,0:55:51.05,default,,0,0,0,,On the first day, Tokuhain Sakurai is the interviewer and Tokuhain Wakatsuki is the cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:53.39,default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.65,0:55:57.41,default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.41,0:55:59.81,default,,0,0,0,,What song did you two choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.81,0:56:02.09,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, today!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.09,0:56:05.37,default,,0,0,0,,My song is called KOROGATTA KANE O NARASE
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.37,0:56:07.33,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.33,0:56:10.89,default,,0,0,0,,I run around a lot and do a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.89,0:56:11.85,default,,0,0,0,,I want to try that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.85,0:56:13.61,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.61,0:56:20.29,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd do it with a song like that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.29,0:56:22.97,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's very unexpected, but I might want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.97,0:56:25.21,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.57,0:56:26.91,default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.91,0:56:31.57,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so I'm dancing with excitement, so please don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.57,0:56:33.95,default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's go to the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.95,0:56:35.25,default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.25,0:56:38.25,default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.29,0:56:40.31,default,,0,0,0,,I'm eating rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.51,0:56:49.21,default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person who doesn't eat at all when I'm on stage, but I'm really hungry today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.05,0:56:55.15,default,,0,0,0,,ZEN IN CENTER project, Saito-san is in charge of the sun knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.61,0:57:01.59,default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time, so I hope I can get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.69,0:57:07.57,default,,0,0,0,,The song is also an exciting song, so I think it's suitable for the first song.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.13,0:57:08.83,default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.47,0:57:11.03,default,,0,0,0,,Mi-o-na-tana
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.45,0:57:12.33,default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.92,0:57:14.62,default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.38,0:57:24.84,default,,0,0,0,,I'm very nervous, but the Budokan is a wonderful place, so I want to do my best so that everyone can have a good live.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.34,0:57:27.34,default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool to be in the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.34,0:57:31.34,default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine who would be able to come this far in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.34,0:57:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.02,0:57:35.02,default,,0,0,0,,This is the goal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.02,0:57:37.02,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.02,0:57:39.02,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.02,0:57:41.02,default,,0,0,0,,It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.02,0:57:43.02,default,,0,0,0,,I'm really curious about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.02,0:57:45.02,default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.02,0:57:47.02,default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.02,0:57:49.02,default,,0,0,0,,After this, I hate you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.02,0:57:53.02,default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who will be the center today?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.02,0:57:55.02,default,,0,0,0,,I will do it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.02,0:58:01.02,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the center today because I lied to Tossa that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.02,0:58:07.02,default,,0,0,0,,Last year's ARIAKE was the main song.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.02,0:58:12.02,default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to surpass last year's ARIAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.02,0:58:14.02,default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.56,0:58:18.26,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nagashima is the first member to know about the beginning of Under Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.62,0:58:20.04,default,,0,0,0,,The engine of the Cayenne Miner
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.48,0:58:23.48,default,,0,0,0,,We keep saying the same thing over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.97,0:58:25.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.44,0:58:27.90,default,,0,0,0,,This is the last round of the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.09,0:58:31.81,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it so that we can show you great things together!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.23,0:58:35.73,default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.25,0:58:38.25,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.45,0:58:42.45,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.58,0:58:47.34,default,,0,0,0,,Their dream, the Budokan Live, is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.57,0:59:48.57,default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the game, the all-center game begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.45,0:59:51.35,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please take a look at the center stage at once!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.37,1:00:43.61,default,,0,0,0,,What are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.46,1:00:48.46,default,,0,0,0,,I'm 23 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.83,1:00:49.71,default,,0,0,0,,Did you watch it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.67,1:02:13.17,default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.31,1:02:14.57,default,,0,0,0,,A certain announcement...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.64,1:02:34.64,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Seira Nagashima
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.11,1:02:35.57,default,,0,0,0,,Nogizaka46
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.87,1:02:36.77,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.53,1:02:42.03,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.27,1:02:43.31,default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.00,1:02:46.00,default,,0,0,0,,To the next dream
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.14,1:02:47.90,default,,0,0,0,,Nagashima Seiru to shite no michi wo
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.22,1:02:49.32,default,,0,0,0,,I chose it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.98,1:02:50.80,default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.26,1:02:52.66,default,,0,0,0,,Nogizaka46
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.93,1:02:53.57,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.27,1:02:57.81,default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of the other members of KAWAIKASHI MIRAI here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.95,1:02:59.95,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.35,1:04:50.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.46,1:04:52.22,default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.51,1:04:54.51,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.85,1:04:59.85,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.37,1:04:59.55,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.26,1:05:09.26,default,,0,0,0,,I want you to do your best, Nogizaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.26,1:05:11.26,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.17,1:05:15.05,default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a better group.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.05,1:05:17.05,default,,0,0,0,,What else do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.05,1:05:19.05,default,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.05,1:05:21.05,default,,0,0,0,,I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.75,1:05:24.11,default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.56,1:05:28.24,default,,0,0,0,,Under Live, Day 2
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.73,1:05:30.23,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.45,1:05:32.45,default,,0,0,0,,See you on the second day!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.96,1:05:33.92,default,,0,0,0,,The second day of UNDERLIVE.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.92,1:05:38.72,default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was the most excited at this venue yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.72,1:05:41.12,default,,0,0,0,,I was confident that I stood out more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.12,1:05:42.06,default,,0,0,0,,It was noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.06,1:05:43.34,default,,0,0,0,,I got a super lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.45,1:05:54.39,default,,0,0,0,,After everyone found it, I was told that it was there, so I would like to enjoy it so much that everyone will find it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.56,1:06:00.56,default,,0,0,0,,On the second day, Tokuhain interviews Tokuhain and Tokuhain intervenes as a cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.83,1:06:03.29,default,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.55,1:06:06.55,default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.55,1:06:09.55,default,,0,0,0,,We're going to perform at the center today.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.55,1:06:10.55,default,,0,0,0,,What song are you going to perform?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.55,1:06:12.55,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to perform for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.55,1:06:15.55,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.55,1:06:17.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kiju-san and Kii-chan are here too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.55,1:06:18.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.55,1:06:19.55,default,,0,0,0,,They look so similar.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.55,1:06:22.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kii-chan, you performed yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.55,1:06:24.55,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I finished yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.55,1:06:26.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kiju-san was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.55,1:06:27.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kiju-san?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.55,1:06:29.55,default,,0,0,0,,Kiju-san was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.55,1:06:33.55,default,,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.43,1:06:36.43,default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.43,1:06:38.43,default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.43,1:06:40.43,default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.43,1:06:42.43,default,,0,0,0,,So today you're going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.43,1:06:44.43,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the center today.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.43,1:06:46.43,default,,0,0,0,,What song are you going to do today?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.43,1:06:48.43,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be by your side when you can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:50.43,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.43,1:06:52.43,default,,0,0,0,,The center of the fan club is special.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.43,1:06:54.43,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.43,1:06:56.43,default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.43,1:06:58.43,default,,0,0,0,,You're like a conductor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.43,1:07:00.43,default,,0,0,0,,I was doing a part-time job yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.43,1:07:02.43,default,,0,0,0,,Reika, I think the camera suits you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:04.43,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.43,1:07:06.43,default,,0,0,0,,The staff asked me if I could take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.43,1:07:08.43,default,,0,0,0,,This is only three minutes long.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.43,1:07:10.43,default,,0,0,0,,I'm desperate.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.43,1:07:12.43,default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.00,1:07:14.00,default,,0,0,0,,Kimen-chan, Mikke-!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.27,1:07:17.27,default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't listen to it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.27,1:07:18.27,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.27,1:07:20.27,default,,0,0,0,,Today, do you have a center?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.27,1:07:21.27,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.27,1:07:23.27,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Haru's melody.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.25,1:07:28.25,default,,0,0,0,,We've decided on a lot of MCs as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.25,1:07:31.25,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.58,1:07:37.58,default,,0,0,0,,Among the members, she has become a big sister, so that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.58,1:07:40.58,default,,0,0,0,,Hime-tan has a good voice, so I love her voice when she was an MC.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.58,1:07:42.58,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm happy. I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.58,1:07:44.58,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.58,1:07:49.58,default,,0,0,0,,On this day, the members who had previously appeared in the Under Live came to support them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.58,1:07:51.58,default,,0,0,0,,They're having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.22,1:07:55.32,default,,0,0,0,,Let's listen to the story of the start of the Under Live.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.58,1:07:57.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's a bonus at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.21,1:07:58.95,default,,0,0,0,,I did it as a bonus for the handshake party.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.95,1:08:02.67,default,,0,0,0,,After the handshake party, I watched it in Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.67,1:08:05.85,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone came to see the movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.85,1:08:10.65,default,,0,0,0,,The members were the most excited when the fans were there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.65,1:08:14.51,default,,0,0,0,,MINAMI said this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.75,1:08:16.05,default,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.38,1:08:22.58,default,,0,0,0,,When we didn't know each other, we decided to do a vlog together.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.58,1:08:25.70,default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, I was like,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.70,1:08:26.70,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.70,1:08:28.52,default,,0,0,0,,To be honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.89,1:08:30.57,default,,0,0,0,,I was serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.07,1:08:32.07,default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.35,1:08:35.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I came here, and it's been two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.35,1:08:37.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.35,1:08:39.35,default,,0,0,0,,This is what I'm thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.70,1:08:43.40,default,,0,0,0,,The second day of UnderLive has finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.71,1:08:46.17,default,,0,0,0,,The two delivery men also hurried to the seats.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.43,1:08:52.15,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it to the opening yesterday, so I want to make it to the opening today.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.48,1:08:54.48,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.49,1:08:57.49,default,,0,0,0,,The under members are also on standby!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.84,1:09:13.84,default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the next performance!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.31,1:12:19.87,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for finding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.79,1:12:51.79,default,,0,0,0,,Please subscribe to my channel and give it a high rating.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.36,1:12:53.36,default,,0,0,0,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.98,1:13:10.90,default,,0,0,0,,Mia-chan...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.96,1:13:14.96,default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.38,1:13:18.38,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.60,1:13:20.88,default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of our report for the past 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.88,1:13:21.88,default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.69,1:13:24.91,default,,0,0,0,,It was a fun live.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.18,1:13:27.18,default,,0,0,0,,We have to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.18,1:13:29.18,default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.18,1:13:31.18,default,,0,0,0,,We got a lot of power, so let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.29,1:13:31.95,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.19,1:13:37.27,default,,0,0,0,,That's all for Nagizaka 46 Under Live!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.76,1:13:38.92,default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.77,1:13:52.53,default,,0,0,0,,And the second member of the lecture room is...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.96,1:13:55.30,default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.77,1:13:57.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.55,1:14:00.05,default,,0,0,0,,NANCHO
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.80,1:14:02.80,default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.80,1:14:04.80,default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.95,1:14:10.93,default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to talk one-on-one like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.77,1:14:12.27,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.57,1:14:13.85,default,,0,0,0,,Just once,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.98,1:14:14.48,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.01,1:14:17.17,default,,0,0,0,,When I went somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.53,1:14:18.53,default,,0,0,0,,Airplane
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.10,1:14:20.46,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.93,1:14:22.61,default,,0,0,0,,There was a seat next to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.61,1:14:24.95,default,,0,0,0,,And together...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.44,1:14:25.94,default,,0,0,0,,game
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.88,1:14:28.56,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.93,1:14:31.19,default,,0,0,0,,I rode it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.39,1:14:33.09,default,,0,0,0,,We played the game without sleeping for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.09,1:14:34.79,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.79,1:14:36.49,default,,0,0,0,,I think we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.49,1:14:37.69,default,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.69,1:14:38.29,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.29,1:14:39.59,default,,0,0,0,,It was when everyone was sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.59,1:14:39.89,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.89,1:14:41.49,default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.49,1:14:43.09,default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.39,1:14:45.17,default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.47,1:14:47.75,default,,0,0,0,,There was such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.35,1:14:48.85,default,,0,0,0,,a ring
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.25,1:14:50.75,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.91,1:14:52.91,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.00,1:14:54.16,default,,0,0,0,,But they talk, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.40,1:14:55.64,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.82,1:14:58.62,default,,0,0,0,,I will talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.78,1:15:00.78,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.78,1:15:02.78,default,,0,0,0,,Reika is the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.33,1:15:04.49,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.28,1:15:05.88,default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.62,1:15:07.12,default,,0,0,0,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.13,1:15:07.97,default,,0,0,0,,I'm being teased.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.19,1:15:12.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this as a captain, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.69,1:15:16.21,default,,0,0,0,,Nana is one of the members
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.61,1:15:17.73,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the only...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.85,1:15:19.99,default,,0,0,0,,For Raker,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.61,1:15:22.49,default,,0,0,0,,They'll come, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.59,1:15:23.87,default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.00,1:15:25.68,default,,0,0,0,,But Reika is...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.53,1:15:27.91,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.21,1:15:31.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's a little annoying.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.65,1:15:32.55,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.02,1:15:35.82,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm the one who's happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.09,1:15:37.15,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.44,1:15:38.30,default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.07,1:15:40.43,default,,0,0,0,,I don't even use my ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.09,1:15:41.59,default,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.37,1:15:45.97,default,,0,0,0,,That's a good thing. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.14,1:15:48.52,default,,0,0,0,,I think she's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.86,1:15:51.72,default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me and didn't say anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.06,1:15:55.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look down at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.61,1:15:57.99,default,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.37,1:16:02.17,default,,0,0,0,,First of all, this time it's called Kouhaku Special
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.49,1:16:03.47,default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.97,1:16:06.27,default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.62,1:16:07.96,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.51,1:16:10.03,default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long day.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.49,1:16:11.11,default,,0,0,0,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.45,1:16:14.63,default,,0,0,0,,It was very deep.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.10,1:16:16.74,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a bit bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.86,1:16:17.62,default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.95,1:16:19.51,default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.61,1:16:20.33,default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.48,1:16:22.68,default,,0,0,0,,But it was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.81,1:16:23.97,default,,0,0,0,,It was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.97,1:16:25.47,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the atmosphere was...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.05,1:16:27.23,default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.49,1:16:29.01,default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's amazing that I was able to come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.25,1:16:30.79,default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.68,1:16:36.62,default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it makes much sense if it's just once.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.53,1:16:38.03,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.14,1:16:38.96,default,,0,0,0,,When I was told that,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.52,1:16:43.12,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told when I was gathered.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.26,1:16:44.88,default,,0,0,0,,This year, Nogizaka Kohaku
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.09,1:16:47.09,default,,0,0,0,,It comes out like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.39,1:16:48.73,default,,0,0,0,,At that moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.59,1:16:53.53,default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely, just once
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.89,1:16:55.89,default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would never make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.00,1:16:57.10,default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.57,1:17:00.75,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought as soon as I heard the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.96,1:17:05.34,default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.47,1:17:06.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.23,1:17:08.47,default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.73,1:17:11.53,default,,0,0,0,,Now Kouhaku is over
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.81,1:17:17.31,default,,0,0,0,,I was happy to be in the group this year, but I want to be a group that can be in the group next year and the year after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.31,1:17:21.05,default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of members who say that in interviews.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.72,1:17:26.14,default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I heard it for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.43,1:17:28.61,default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that your thoughts come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.18,1:17:30.38,default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.59,1:17:31.57,default,,0,0,0,,It's so fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.67,1:17:42.33,default,,0,0,0,,You've changed a lot since the beginning, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.58,1:17:47.18,default,,0,0,0,,I think I have a lot of experiences, especially at the center.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.61,1:17:50.95,default,,0,0,0,,I think they're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.10,1:17:54.00,default,,0,0,0,,Since when did it change? After the center?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.43,1:17:56.11,default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.45,1:18:00.27,default,,0,0,0,,When I realized it, it was the first time I had one thought in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.83,1:18:02.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to apply it on the center of my face.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.17,1:18:02.83,default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.13,1:18:04.43,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.77,1:18:06.77,default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was a hit wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.88,1:18:07.88,default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.88,1:18:08.88,default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.88,1:18:09.88,default,,0,0,0,,Bungee jumping
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.88,1:18:10.88,default,,0,0,0,,I think I did my best
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.88,1:18:12.88,default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.28,1:18:13.78,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.76,1:18:14.96,default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's really...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.68,1:18:17.00,default,,0,0,0,,so big
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.82,1:18:18.88,default,,0,0,0,,I highly recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.36,1:18:22.36,default,,0,0,0,,Bungie? Macau's Bungie, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.36,1:18:23.36,default,,0,0,0,,I highly recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.36,1:18:24.36,default,,0,0,0,,It's the highest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.36,1:18:26.36,default,,0,0,0,,But I recommend it to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.33,1:18:28.39,default,,0,0,0,,It flies really well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.93,1:18:33.31,default,,0,0,0,,Because of my anxiety and fear,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.11,1:18:34.73,default,,0,0,0,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.97,1:18:37.93,default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the result is...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.57,1:18:44.57,default,,0,0,0,,I think I've become more confident about myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.57,1:18:46.67,default,,0,0,0,,So after that, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.68,1:18:49.52,default,,0,0,0,,I was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.05,1:18:52.21,default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.48,1:18:57.02,default,,0,0,0,,I was under a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.44,1:18:58.32,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.42,1:19:00.12,default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.22,1:19:01.18,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.69,1:19:03.13,default,,0,0,0,,Like, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.29,1:19:04.65,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.83,1:19:05.95,default,,0,0,0,,It changed so fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.56,1:19:08.56,default,,0,0,0,,......
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.93,1:19:08.43,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.38,1:19:09.38,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.60,1:19:10.10,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.40,1:19:14.80,default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely different, but she seems to have a lot of room.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.17,1:19:15.93,default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.57,1:19:17.97,default,,0,0,0,,again and again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.20,1:19:19.76,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.87,1:19:22.35,default,,0,0,0,,the front and the center
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.65,1:19:23.45,default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.58,1:19:24.38,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.92,1:19:28.80,default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I say getting used to it,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.21,1:19:31.21,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's because of the music
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.06,1:19:35.40,default,,0,0,0,,I think she's moving on to the next step.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.97,1:19:39.81,default,,0,0,0,,It's not about whether you can be in the center or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.22,1:19:40.72,default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.01,1:19:44.65,default,,0,0,0,,What do you personally think?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.93,1:19:45.81,default,,0,0,0,,Gong-gu
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.21,1:19:48.95,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nanase?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.76,1:19:51.42,default,,0,0,0,,I want to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.67,1:19:54.25,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.16,1:19:57.80,default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmmmm...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.97,1:19:59.91,default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.13,1:20:02.81,default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm in a group.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.97,1:20:04.47,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.96,1:20:06.88,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.77,1:20:09.95,default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.11,1:20:10.87,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.61,1:20:12.31,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.54,1:20:14.64,default,,0,0,0,,What I want to do is...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.75,1:20:16.13,default,,0,0,0,,Animal work.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.29,1:20:23.23,default,,0,0,0,,I really like the work of animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.32,1:20:24.82,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.60,1:20:28.60,default,,0,0,0,,with animals that have something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.28,1:20:30.42,default,,0,0,0,,I got a hard job.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.72,1:20:32.98,default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I wish I could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.21,1:20:34.85,default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.61,1:20:37.61,default,,0,0,0,,I can do it, bang bang
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.61,1:20:39.61,default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.61,1:20:41.61,default,,0,0,0,,You can do it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.47,1:20:43.41,default,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.58,1:20:46.86,default,,0,0,0,,I don't really say what I like
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.10,1:20:50.58,default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type of girl who's all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.36,1:20:54.46,default,,0,0,0,,I get bored of my own face.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.13,1:20:55.63,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.63,1:20:56.39,default,,0,0,0,,There's that thing
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.39,1:20:56.89,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.96,1:20:58.96,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.60,1:20:58.10,default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.21,1:20:58.91,default,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.91,1:20:59.51,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.16,1:21:00.92,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.12,1:21:02.90,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a bully.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.42,1:21:10.06,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm getting tired of looking at the mirror when I'm doing my make-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.78,1:21:17.24,default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of watching it, so I'll just watch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.76,1:21:20.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't fully understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.48,1:21:27.16,default,,0,0,0,,Make-up is also popular, and there are also things that are popular among themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.26,1:21:29.02,default,,0,0,0,,It's not about being particular about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.02,1:21:30.08,default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.08,1:21:31.08,default,,0,0,0,,That's also...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.58,1:21:33.14,default,,0,0,0,,I have to be aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.50,1:21:34.54,default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.71,1:21:38.81,default,,0,0,0,,I was like, this is good enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.68,1:21:40.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.41,1:21:42.15,default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.56,1:21:47.38,default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about changing the shape of my eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.97,1:21:48.83,default,,0,0,0,,Well, today...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.66,1:21:52.14,default,,0,0,0,,I want to make the middle part thicker.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.29,1:21:53.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.24,1:21:55.68,default,,0,0,0,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.54,1:21:58.04,default,,0,0,0,,The freshness is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:22:02.12,default,,0,0,0,,I've been told that it's important.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.53,1:22:04.91,default,,0,0,0,,It's not always the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.24,1:22:07.18,default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.65,1:22:09.95,default,,0,0,0,,Nagisaka is a girl group.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.14,1:22:15.08,default,,0,0,0,,I've recently been told that it's a good group, but I'm rushing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.23,1:22:19.79,default,,0,0,0,,I think she is one of the most important members of the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.06,1:22:21.62,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.08,1:22:23.00,default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.23,1:22:25.37,default,,0,0,0,,I want you to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.57,1:22:55.55,default,,0,0,0,,Translated by Releska
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.83,1:22:29.33,default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.11,1:22:32.11,default,,0,0,0,,It looks like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.11,1:22:33.37,default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.95,1:22:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,I talked to you as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.95,1:22:39.15,default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.49,1:22:42.89,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.89,1:22:44.63,default,,0,0,0,,Is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.57,1:22:47.57,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.01,1:22:49.43,default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, 46!
